<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #3b82f6;
            --primary-dark: #1d4ed8;
            --primary-light: #eff6ff;
            --gray-50: #f9fafb;
            --gray-100: #f3f4f6;
            --gray-200: #e5e7eb;
            --gray-600: #4b5563;
            --gray-700: #374151;
            --gray-800: #1f2937;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--gray-50);
            color: var(--gray-700);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .about-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 3rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            margin-top: -60px;
        }

        .section-title {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .content-text {
            line-height: 1.8;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .feature-item {
            padding: 2rem;
            background: var(--gray-50);
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body, html { overflow-x: hidden; max-width: 100vw; }
            .about-hero {
                padding: 40px 20px;
            }

            .card {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
                margin-top: -30px;
            }

            .section-title {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .feature-item {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            .button-group {
                flex-direction: column;
                width: 100%;
            }

            .button-group a {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/public-header') %>
    <div class="about-hero">
        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; opacity: 0.9; margin: 0;">Transforming Public Service Experiences</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="content-text">
                At QueuePro, we believe that your time is valuable. Our mission is to eliminate the frustration of long
                waiting lines at government offices and public service centers. By leveraging smart technology, we
                provide transparent, real-time queue management that respects the citizen's schedule.
            </p>

            <h2 class="section-title">Why QueuePro?</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock feature-icon"></i>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Real-time Tracking</h3>
                    <p>Monitor your position in the queue from anywhere using your smartphone.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt feature-icon"></i>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Digital Tokens</h3>
                    <p>Generate tokens digitally and receive notifications when it's your turn.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line feature-icon"></i>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Smart Analytics</h3>
                    <p>Helping administrators optimize service delivery through data-driven insights.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 4rem; text-align: center;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Ready to get started?</h2>
                <div class="button-group" style="display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:1rem; margin-top:2rem;">
                    <a href="/"
                        style="text-decoration:none; padding:1rem 2rem; background:var(--primary); color:white; border-radius:0.5rem; font-weight:600;">Back
                        to Home</a>
                    <a href="/contact"
                        style="text-decoration:none; padding:1rem 2rem; border:2px solid var(--primary); color:var(--primary); border-radius:0.5rem; font-weight:600;">Contact
                        Support</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer style="text-align: center; padding: 40px 20px; color: var(--gray-600); font-size: 0.9rem;">
        &copy; 2024 QueuePro - Queue Management System. All rights reserved.
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/mobile-menu.js"></script>
    <%- include('partials/scroll-to-top') %>
</body>

</html>